{"tid":972902,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)天賦的禮物 希魔撞正殺人狂","createTime":"2019-01-07T17:11:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T21:05:48.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ebb77025c6df1d8c1e340f036ec1350f4fe31a64","tid":972902,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T17:11:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=V7LlLSrrJUberb4%2Fsy9RMUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=6729c439\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=V7LlLSrrJUberb4%2Fsy9RMUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=f11689a0\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=V7LlLSrrJUberb4%2Fsy9RMUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=9c2d923d\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/4/47/Gifted_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F4%2F47%2FGifted_Poster.jpg&h=fb83badb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/81/Inglourious_Basterds_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F81%2FInglourious_Basterds_Poster.jpg&h=90efad21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.在一座佛羅里達州中部的小鎮，七歲的瑪麗在她入學的第一天展現卓越的數學天份。她獲得一筆獎學金供她到專收天才兒童的私立學校就讀，但他的舅舅拒絕接受。他之所以如此，乃因瑪麗的母親曾經是極有前途的數學家，自殺之前致力於納維&ndash;斯托克斯問題（尚未被破解千禧年大獎難題之一）當時瑪麗六個月大。從那時起她的舅舅法蘭克便擔任瑪麗實際上的監護人。他堅信他的妹妹會希望瑪麗過「正常的」童年..<br />\n<br />\n2.在二次大戰期間德占區的法國，外號「猶太獵人」（The Jew Hunter）的親衛隊上校漢斯&middot;蘭達（Hans Landa，克里斯多夫&middot;華茲飾）在一位法國奶農皮埃爾&middot;拉帕提（Perrier LaPadite）的家中審問他。拉帕提為了家人的安全供認了猶太裔的德瑞芙斯（Dreyfus）一家就藏在他家的地板下。蘭達讓親衛隊士兵隔著地板掃射殺害了這一家人，但少女蘇珊娜（Shosanna，梅蘭妮&middot;羅蘭飾）僥倖逃脫<br />\n<br />\n1 15AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=V7LlLSrrJUberb4%2Fsy9RMUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=82f88935\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=V7LlLSrrJUberb4%2Fsy9RMUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=34c1f388\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a>裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8b41e93c97c9a78ba1c1318ba77c698ddc4f5b0","tid":972902,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T17:19:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d38b5afa2b7cb5f1fc6f0a812fa710ff288a6c11","tid":972902,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T17:40:30.000Z","msg"